<br>
<br>
On the topic of New stuff... heard that a really cool thing is being tried out on Test Server and should make it to us all soon in a patch... Two more Bank Slots. Now I know.. big deal you say.. two more slots, 20 more places withs bags in them. Kicker that makes them so cool... the two slots will be shared by all your toons on that server. That means... I get a nifty plus 10 wis, Roar of Winter procing club on a raid with Tiger. I hit a bank, toss the club into a bag in those two slots, and camp out. Awaken Tigger, hit the bank and pull the club out! Woot! No more needing to bother folks for transfers. It will be limited, as No drop items will not be allowed in those slots, as well as if any of your up to 8 toons has a lore item that same lore item won't be able to go in those slots. I haven't heard yet how this is working with coin... If there is a second coin pool all toons can access or if you simply take a small loss in resale value and buy gems to share coin between toons... (ie... for both Tiger and Tigger.. Peridots can be sold to Vendors for 9.5 Plat... and can be bought for 11 easy way to share cash at a slight loss if no one is about to do a coin transfer).<br>
<br>
Hmmmm... Not so happy news off the test server..<br>
<br>
Under 45's no longer being affected by group or Mass buffs of any kind that are over level 50 spells. ie... no more C3, POTG, Ageo, etc.... If you have Mid level toons and use this stuff... (coughs and glances over at Tigger) Better level dang fast to 45 or start learning NOW to do without... Next Patch is scheduled for June 4th... That may be the day...<br>
<br>
